('university', 'FUTO QS 201', 'Building Measurement', 'Linear measurement of skirting boards is taken along:', 'mcq', '["The top edge", "The bottom edge", "The centre line", "Both edges"]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Skirting is measured along the centre line of the board.', 'medium', 2022, 'Federal University of Technology Owerri', 'QS 201'),
