('university', 'ABU QS 401', 'Building Measurement', 'Which of these is measured in linear metres?', 'mcq', '["Floor tiling", "Wall plastering", "Damp proof course", "Concrete slab"]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Damp proof course (DPC) is measured in linear metres.', 'easy', 2018, 'Ahmadu Bello University', 'QS 401'),
