('university', 'LAUTECH QS 302', 'Cost Planning', 'The cube method of estimation uses:', 'mcq', '["Floor area x height", "Length x width x overall height", "Perimeter x floor area", "Number of storeys x floor area"]'::jsonb, 'B', 'The cube method estimates cost using the overall volume (L x W x H) of the building.', 'medium', 2021, 'Ladoke Akintola University', 'QS 302'),
