('university', 'UNILAG QS 311', 'Tendering', 'The purpose of tendering in construction is to:', 'mcq', '["Select the cheapest contractor", "Obtain competitive prices for carrying out the work", "Avoid contracts", "Eliminate competition"]'::jsonb, 'B', 'Tendering obtains competitive prices from qualified contractors for the works.', 'easy', 2020, 'University of Lagos', 'QS 311'),
